(1668, 43, '_simple_fields_fieldGroupID_23_fieldID_1_numInSet_0', 'MAINS'),
(1669, 43, '_simple_fields_fieldGroupID_23_fieldID_2_numInSet_0', '<p>Our meat is sourced from producers across australia with an importance on quality our head chef, lachy cashman, has a long and detailed history with butchery, growing up on a cattle farm and following in the footsteps of his family trade we are continually looking for the choicest, most premium meat available the preparation of our meat includes dry aging our beef in a temperature and humidity controlled room.<br />\nBy dry aging the beef it concentrates the flavour and increases the tenderness, enabling us to provide you with the highest quality possible.<br />\nmarket &amp; co 180 grain fed eye fillet 220gm, darling downs, queensland 40<br />\n400 day grain fed wagyu 7-9+ 250gm rump, diamintina, queensland 39<br />\nbeef city black 120 day grain fed scotch 350gm, toowoomba, queensland 41<br />\nrangers valley 300 day grain fed sirloin 350gm, glen innes, new south wales 39<br />\nsteaks are pan roasted in beef fat, accompanied by burnt onion puree, mushroom pate, duck fat potato</p>\n'),
